{"id": 3212, "date": "2012-01-15T11:00:22", "date_gmt": "2012-01-15T19:00:22", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=3212"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T09:37:13", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-24T16:37:13", "slug": "cover-me-jimmy-lafave-land-of-hope-and-dreams", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2012/01/15/cover-me-jimmy-lafave-land-of-hope-and-dreams/", "title": {"rendered": "Jimmy LaFave: Land of Hope and Dreams"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Oklahoma singer-songwriter Jimmy LaFave has a talent for interpreting Bruce&#8217;s songs. (See his cover of &#8220;Valentine&#8217;s Day&#8221;.)</p>\n<p>In 2012, Jimmy released his album\u00a0<em>Depending on the Distance</em>, featuring his cover of Bruce&#8217;s &#8220;Land of Hope and Dreams.&#8221; Unlike Bruce&#8217;s version, which plays more like a declarative anthem, Jimmy&#8217;s version is a tender and intimate love song. It&#8217;s a different take, and a great cover.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FoVYbBGXHvI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>\u00a9 July 20, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Jimmy LaFave&#8217;s cover of Bruce&#8217;s &#8220;Land of Hope and Dreams&#8221; is more tender than the original&#8211;less anthemic, but equally idealistic.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 3390, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_track